      "category": "team",
      "content": "A vulnerability was discovered in Cloudflare\u2019s User Deletion process which resulted in the current session not being terminated when a request to delete the user had been submitted. Cloudflare\u2019s Engineering Team have fixed the vulnerability and user sessions are now invalidated once a user account deletion request is received.",
